Solution to Firts letter capital challenge
It has a good test coverage



1.) To setup: Enter npm install at the terminal of root solution(cd challenge_1_solution)
npm install

2.) To run test enter npm run test, it uses jest for assertions and sinon for stubbing
npm run test


3) To use library, just require it and call the isFirstLetterUpper function

const isCapital = require('./index');
isCapital.isFirstLetterUpper("Sola") => true
isCapital.isFirstLetterUpper("sola") => false
isCapital.isFirstLetterUpper() => should throw error